236 inline SpellSchools GetFirstSchoolInMask(SpellSchoolMask mask)
237 {
238  for (int i = 0; i < MAX_SPELL_SCHOOL; ++i)
239  if (mask & (1 << i))
240  return SpellSchools(i);
241 
242  return SPELL_SCHOOL_NORMAL;
243 }

1618 inline SkillType SkillByLockType(LockType locktype)
1619 {
1620  switch (locktype)
1621  {
1622  case LOCKTYPE_PICKLOCK: return SKILL_LOCKPICKING;
1623  case LOCKTYPE_HERBALISM: return SKILL_HERBALISM;
1624  case LOCKTYPE_MINING: return SKILL_MINING;
1625  case LOCKTYPE_FISHING: return SKILL_FISHING;
1626  case LOCKTYPE_INSCRIPTION: return SKILL_INSCRIPTION;
1627  default: break;
1628  }
1629  return SKILL_NONE;
1630 }
